<p><strong>Note from the future</strong>: <em>I believe that this one event sparked a butterfly effect. I feel it has had a considerable impact on my life choices pertaining towards WnCC, shaping my interests and pursuing coding as a hobby. I look back to this with a vivid memory and great pleasure.</em></p>
